The paper discusses active learning in the context of overparameterized models, which is a common topic in the machine learning community. The use of kernel-based methods and neural networks also suggests that the paper may fall under the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the mention of cluster structure in unlabeled data suggests that the paper may also fall under the categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the mention of experiments with kernel methods suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision).
